title: Check out our amazing location! 1 bed, 1 bath. Stoneleigh at the Reserve
posting_body: ['Stoneleigh at the Reserve', '5200 Annapolis Ln N', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'A wonderful home in Plymouth is waiting for you!', 'We currently have a gorgeous 1 bedroom 1 bathroom renting for $1685 - $1795 per month.', 'This unit comes with 1016 sq ft.', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'show contact info', 'Community Highlights:', '− Bike Storage', '− Coffee Station', '− Conference Room', '− Elevator', '− Fitness Center', '− Free Weights', '− Gameroom', '− Picnic Area', '− Pool', '− Resident Lounge', '− Barbecue/Grill Area', '− Business Center', '− Cardio Machines', '− Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '− Controlled Access Building', '− Disposal Chutes', '− On-site Maintenance & Management', '− Planned Social Activities', '− Racquetball Court', '− Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'Unit Highlights:', '− Air Conditioning', '− Ceiling Fans', 'In Select Units', '− Dining Room', '− Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '− Garbage Disposal', '− Linen Closet', '− Microwave', '− Pantry In Select Units', '− Patio/Balcony', 'In Select Units', '− Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'Contact:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Leasing Options:', 'Variable', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Management:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '8A59AE630F1F447']
